alert.note: Alert for Liberty; Wakulla (Florida) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 20 at 7:13PM EDT until August 20 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Tallahassee
info.description: The National Weather Service in Tallahassee has issued a * Severe Thunderstorm Warning for... Northwestern Wakulla County in Big Bend Florida... Southern Liberty County in Big Bend Florida... * Until 800 PM EDT. * At 713 PM EDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 21 miles west of Crawfordville, moving west at 25 mph. HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts. SOURCE...Radar indicated. IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees. * Locations impacted include... Orange, East Camp, Jewel Fire Tower, Vilas, Jensen Place, Central City, Red Hill, Clio, Poplar Camp, Smith Creek, Estiffanulga, Kern, Wilma, Lewis, Woods, Nixon Garden, and Twin Pole. HAIL THREAT...RADAR INDICATED MAX HAIL SIZE...<.75 IN WIND THREAT...RADAR INDICATED MAX WIND GUST...60 MPH
info.instruction: For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a building.
